## YOUR TASK NOW

Provide your evaluation following the methodology above.

1. Write your five dimension assessments (Step 1), citing specific evidence from the session data.
2. Write your holistic narrative and score (Step 2).

End your response with the total score as a standalone number on the very last line.
The last line must contain ONLY the number — no formatting, no markdown, no text.
Example: if the total score is 62, the last line should be exactly:
62


